# Monetization and Economy Rules

Monetization must not break trust or balance.

Allowed directions:
- rewarded ads
- remove ads
- cosmetics
- starter bundles
- season pass
- limited convenience boosts
- bonus chests
- optional revives with strict caps

Avoid:
- pay-to-win PvP
- unlimited paid revives
- dark patterns
- fake scarcity
- client-side purchase entitlement grants
- client-side premium currency grants

Economy rules:
- rewards must be server-validated where meaningful
- purchases must be idempotent
- duplicate reward claims must be prevented
- shop offers must use server/Firebase-defined price and reward data
- never trust client-submitted reward amounts

Ad rules:
- do not show interstitials during active battle turns
- prefer rewarded ads at natural decision points
- respect consent/privacy requirements
- keep ad cadence configurable remotely
